ss="css-fzudtj"><div class="chakra-container css-vp2g1e" data-component="ProductView" data-testid="product-view"><script data-testid="product-schema" type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org/","@type":"Product","name":"Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Fragment x Travis Scott Sail Military Blue","description":"The Jordan 1 Retro Low Fragment x Travis Scott Sail Military Blue represents the intersection of three worlds — hip-hop, Japanese streetwear, and Jordan heritage — all meeting on one iconic silhouette. Dressed in sail, black, muslin, and military blue, this pair blends Fragment’s minimalist precision with Travis Scott’s rebellious edge. The reversed Swoosh, a signature Cactus Jack touch, immediately sets it apart, while Fragment’s lightning bolt logo adds a seal of approval that only Hiroshi Fujiwara could bring.<br><br>This isn’t just another collaboration; it’s a cultural timestamp. Travis Scott’s previous Jordan releases defined modern hype culture, while Fragment’s legacy stretches back to the early 2000s roots of global streetwear. Together, they bridge generations, where the rugged authenticity of Travis’ aesthetic meets Fragment’s technical polish. The premium leather construction, aged midsole finish, and carefully balanced palette give the sneaker a museum-worthy feel with everyday wearability.<br><br>When the Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Fragment x Travis Scott Sail Military Blue released, it retailed for $155 and dropped on November 15, 2025. Combining two creative giants with Jordan Brand’s most beloved silhouette, it quickly became one of the most hyped and collectible sneakers of the year. This sneaker is a fusion of artistry, attitude, and legacy that commands attention on and off the timeline.","image":"https://images.stockx.com/images/Air-Jordan-1-Retro-Low-OG-SP-Fragment-x-Travis-Scott-Sail-Military-Blue-Product-v2.jpg?fit=fill&bg=FFFFFF&w=1200&h=857&q=60&dpr=1&trim=color&updated_at=1764344728","releaseDate":"2025-11-15","model":"Jordan 