s includes the import duties required for products to enter the country, this is an estimated amount","import_duties_verification_tooltip":"This fee makes it possible for StockX to process every item on our platform using a rigorous multi-step process so you can shop with confidence. This also includes the import duties required for products to enter the country, this is an estimated amount","Included":"Included","Included Accessories":"Included Accessories","Infant":"Infant","influencer_list_meta_description":"Click to check out this collection of items on StockX!","Instagram":"Instagram","international_seller_pane_button_text":"Got It","international_seller_pane_message":"Sorry about that, but right now this product isn't available in your country. Keep an eye on the StockX blog and newsletter for international updates!","international_seller_pane_title":"You're not from around here, are you?","intl_ddu_disclaimer":"Import duties and taxes are NOT included in the price and the buyer may be required to pay duties and taxes upon delivery","invalid_ccic_error":"Please enter a valid CCIC.","It doesn’t get any easier":"It doesn’t get any easier.","It doesn’t get any easier.":"It doesn’t get any easier.","Italian":"Italian","Item":"Item","item":"item","Item Received for Authentication":"Item Received for Verification","itemized_ddp_fee_tooltip":"This includes processing fees for payment processing and verification of products","itemized_ddp_fee_tooltip_verification":"This includes verification fees for payment processing and verification of products","Items":"Items","items":"items","January":"January","Jobs":"Jobs","Jordan 1":"Jordan 1","Jordan 1 Retro":"Jordan 1 Retro","Jordan 11 Retro":"Jordan 11 Retro","July":"July","June":"June","Language":"Language","Last Name":"Last Name","Last Sale":"Last Sale","Last Sale:":"Last Sale:","Last Updated":"Last Updated","Last Updated:":"Last Updated:","Latest News":"Latest News","Learn More":"Learn More","learn_more_about_conditions"