authenticator.","order_status_timeline_sub_stockx_received_incomplete":"It typically takes 1-3 days for your order to arrive at StockX.","order_status_timeline_sub_authentic_incomplete":"Once everything is StockX Verified, we'll pack it up for shipping to you","order_status_timeline_sub_authentic":"Congrats, your order is StockX Verified! We're packing it up for you now.","order_status_timeline_sub_staged_outbound_incomplete":"Once everything with your order is packed and labeled, it'll be ready for the carrier to pick up.","order_status_timeline_sub_staged_outbound":"We've packed up your order and are just waiting for the carrier to pick it up","order_status_timeline_sub_shipped_outbound_incomplete":"Your tracking link will appear here after it's shipped","order_status_timeline_sub_shipped_outbound":"Track your order here:","order_status_timeline_sub_delivered_incomplete":"Don't forget to use #GotItOnStockX when sharing unboxings.","order_status_timeline_sub_delivered":"Enjoy! Don't forget to use #GotItOnStockX when sharing unboxing pics","order_status_timeline_sub_return_started":"Please ship your item back to StockX ASAP!","order_status_timeline_sub_return_shipped_incomplete":"Please check back here for confirmation that StockX has received your return","order_status_timeline_sub_return_shipped":"Thank you for shipping your item. Please check back here for confirmation that StockX has received your return","order_status_timeline_sub_return_received_incomplete":"Once received, our Quality Assurance team will confirm the return","order_status_timeline_sub_return_received":"Thank you! This return has been received by our Quality Assurance team for their review","order_status_timeline_sub_return_completed":"Thank you! Your return has been verified, and we are beginning the refund process. ","order_status_timeline_sub_return_refunded":"We're sorry that your order didn't work out this time. Refunds may take between 3 to 5 business days to hit your account.","order_status_timeline_sub_return_rejected":"Please check your email for next steps from our team","order_status_timeline_sub_linked_order":"We encountered an issue with your original seller and were able to match your order with a new seller at no additional cost. Your order will update after verification.","order_status_timeline_sub_authentication_failed":"We utilize a multi-step verification process to ensure your order is correct. Unfortunately, your order failed verification. We apologize for this inconvenience. You will receive an email update with next steps shortly.","order_status_timeline_sub_refund_failed":"We were unable to complete your refund. Please check your email for next steps.","order_status_timeline_sub_payment_failed":"Please update your payment method to continue shopping","order_status_timeline_sub_donation_complete":"Thank you for your donation!","Other":"Other","Password":"Password","Pay Over Time":"Pay Over Time","Paying with":"Paying with","Payment":"Payment","Payment Failed":"Payment Failed","Payout":"Payout","payout":"payout","Payout Estimate":"Payout Estimate","Payout Info":"Payout Info","Payout issued in USD":"Payout issued in USD","payout_settings_active":"Payout \u003c0\u003eActive\u003c/0\u003e","payout_settings_error_message":"You must enter \u003c0\u003eSeller Info\u003c/0\u003e before you can set up a payout method","payout_settings_inactive":"Payout \u003c0\u003eNot Active\u003c/0\u003e","payout_summary_active":"Payout Method: Active","payout_summary_inactive":"Payout Method: Not Active","PayPal":"PayPal","PayPal Email":"PayPal Email","PayPal Info":"PayPal Info","pdp_add_to_portfolio_or_follow_header":"Add to List","pdp_add_to_portfolio_or_favorite_header":"Add to List","pdp_add_to_list_modal_description":"Lists will help you save, organize, and find your favorite items easily.","pdp_add_to_favorite_placeholder":"Add to...","move_list_placeholder":"Move to...","move_item":"Move Item","list_saved_already":"Saved here already","copy_link":"Copy Link","add_to_different_list":"Add to a Different List","pdp_follow_description":"Save Products You Want to Follow","portfolio_favorite_description":"Save Products You Want to Add to Favorite","pdp_portfolio_description":"Keep Track of Items You Own","pdp_successfully_followed_header":"Successfully Followed Item","pdp_add_to_portfolio_aria_label":"Add To Portfolio","pdp_add_to_portfolio_cancel_button":"Cancel","pdp_add_to_portfolio_choose_condition_header":"Choose Condition","pdp_add_to_portfolio_condition_new":"New","pdp_add_to_portfolio_condition_used":"Used","pdp_add_to_portfolio_confirmation_message":"Added To Portfolio","pdp_removed_from_following_confirmation_message":"Removed From Following","pdp_three_sixty_drag_to_spin":"Drag to spin image","favorite_updated_confirmation_message":"Favorite Updated","favorite_updated_error_message":"Error occurred updating favorite. Please try again.","favorite_confirmation_message":"Added to favorites","favorite_confirmation_subtext":"Make your new favorite item easy to find and organize","favorite_confirmation_link":"See it now","unfavorite_confirmation_link":"Undo","unfavorite_confirmation_message":"{{productTitle}} was Removed From Favorites","move_list_confimration_message":"Item moved.","add_to_list_confimration_message":"Item added to list.","pdp_add_to_portfolio_confirm_button":"Confirm","pdp_add_to_portfolio_grade_picker_error":"You must select a grade.","pdp_add_to_portfolio_header":"Add To Portfolio","pdp_add_to_portfolio_rate_used_condition_header":"Rate Used Condition","pdp_add_to_portfolio_size_picker_error":"You must select a size.","pdp_add_to_portfolio_used_item_disclaimer":"StockX allows you to add used items to your portfolio for market value tracking purposes.","pdp_all_in_asks_disclaimer":"The data below is global and does not include applicable fees calculated at checkout.","pdp_all_in_asks_disclaimer_footer":"The data above is global and does not include applicable fees calculated at checkout.","pdp_all_in_bids_asks_disclaimer_footer_v2":"The prices above do not include applicable fees calculated at checkout.","pdp_all_in_sales_disclaimer_footer":"The prices above do not include applicable fees calculated at checkout. Prices vary depending on the buyer and seller location.","pdp_all_in_sales_disclaimer_header":"The prices below do not include applicable fees calculated at checkout.","pdp_all_in_sales_disclaimer_footer_title":"Do you understand the data shown here?","pdp_all_in_asks_table_primary_text":"* Some prices in this table do not include taxes, duties, and fees so these asks may appear lower than the price displayed to buy this item.","pdp_all_in_asks_table_secondary_text":"We include all taxes, duties and import fees in the item’s Ask price based on where the buyer is located in order to provide the true cost upfront. This helps sellers get a better price in their local market and buyers get lower fees and faster delivery. The data in this table has not been adjusted to include those fees.","pdp_all_in_bids_table_primary_text":"* Some prices in this table do not include taxes, duties, and fees so these bids may appear higher than the price displayed to sell this item.","pdp_all_in_bids_table_secondary_text":"We subtract all duties, taxes and import fees from the item's Bid price based on where the seller is located in order to provide the true payout upfront. This helps sellers get a better price in their local market and buyers get lower fees and faster delivery. The data in this table has not been adjusted to reflect those fees.","pdp_all_in_asks_table_tooltip":"* Some prices are subject to additional fees not included in this table.","pdp_all_in_bids_table_tooltip":"* Some prices are subject to different fees not included in this table.","pdp_all_in_table_tooltip":"* Some prices are subject to additional fees not included in this table.","pdp_all_in_sales_table_primary_text":"The data in this table is global. International sales may include duties, taxes and fees which are not relevant in your location.","pdp_all_in_sales_table_primary_text_v2":"* Some prices in this table include duties, taxes and fees which are not relevant in your location.","pdp_all_in_sales_table_secondary_text":"We add duties, taxes and other import costs into the sale price based on where the buyer and seller are located. This allows us to better match buyers and sellers within the same regions, significantly reducing import duties and taxes. As a result, you may see international sales that are higher than the Lowest Ask or lower than the Highest Bid.","pdp_all_in_sales_table_secondary_text_v2":"We add duties, taxes and other import costs into the price based on where the buyer and seller are located. This allows us to better match buyers and sellers within the same regions, significantly reducing import duties and taxes. As a result, you may see international sales that are higher than the Lowest Ask or lower than the Highest Bid.","pdp_all_in_sales_disclaimer_primary":"We add duties, taxes and other import costs into the price based on where the buyer and seller are located. This allows us to better match buyers and sellers within the same regions, significantly reducing import duties and taxes.","pdp_all_in_sales_disclaimer_secondary_seller":"As a result, sale prices vary around the world and between buyers and sellers. In order to give you the most relevant data, we are showing you sales numbers based on your location and what you would have paid to match with each seller. If you are selling this product \u003c0\u003eswitch to the seller view\u003c/0\u003e.","pdp_all_in_sales_disclaimer_secondary_buyer":"As a result, sale prices vary around the world and between buyers and sellers. In order to give you the most relevant data, we are showing you sales numbers based on your location and the Ask price you would have needed to win each sale. If you are buying this product \u003c0\u003eswitch to the buyer view\u003c/0\u003e.","Xpress Ship":"Xpress Ship","pdp_all_in_sales_table_tooltip_xpress_ship_not_available":"Xpress Ship - Available in select regions only","pdp_all_in_sales_buyer_view_title":"Buyer View","pdp_all_in_sales_seller_view_title":"Seller View","pdp_all_in_sales_buyer_view_description":"Shows the purchase price you would have paid for each sale.","pdp_all_in_sales_seller_view_description":"Shows the Ask price you would have needed to win each sale.","pdp_all_in_sales_seller_view_tooltip":"With Seller View selected, sale prices represent the Ask price you would have needed to win each sale. Use the All Sales table to switch to the Buyer View.","pdp_all_in_sales_disclaimer":"Fees such as duties and taxes may be included in the sale price depending on the buyer and seller location, resulting in different sale prices for Buyers and Sellers.","pdp_all_in_tooltip_dismiss":"Got It","pdp_all_in_is_my_bid_or_ask":"You","pdp_all_in_last_sale_disclaimer":"* This sale is from a different region and includes different fees.","pdp_all_in_sales_graph_disclaimer":"This graph includes international sales which can be subject to different fees.","pdp_all_in_market_history_disclaimer":"This section includes international sales which can be subject to different fees.","pdp_vault_storage_pill":"Vault Storage Available","pdp_below_retail_badge_primary_text":"Price Currently Below Retail","pdp_below_retail_badge_secondary_text":"Get it before it's gone!","pdp_buy_button_text":"Buy","pdp_buy_with_button_text":"Buy with","pdp_buy_button_text_with_amount":"Buy for {{amount}}","pdp_buy_button_text_with_no_amount":"\u003c0\u003e{{leftArrow}}\u003c/0\u003e\u003c1\u003eBuy This Item\u003c/1\u003e","pdp_buy_sell_button_grade_label":"Grade: {{size}}","pdp_buy_sell_button_size_label":"Size: {{size}}","pdp_customer_activity_bid_text":"Your current Bid is {{amount}}","pdp_customer_activity_ask_text":"Your current Ask is {{amount}}","pdp_customer_activity_offer_text":"Your current Offer is {{amount}}","pdp_customer_act