er page.","seller_fee_subtext":"Fee for {{month}}","seller_flex_fee_dropdown_header":"Flex Fee Breakdown","seller_flex_fulfillment_label":"Flex Fulfillment","seller_flex_fulfillment_rate":"{{rate}} per sale","seller_flex_quick_sale_14_days":"Items sold within 14 days","seller_flex_quick_sale_7_days":"Items sold within 7 days","seller_flex_quick_sale_discount_description":"Automatically applied when you sell your Flex items quickly. Time starts after the item is verified.","seller_flex_quick_sale_discount_description_7_days":"Automatically applied when you sell your Flex items within 7 days of being verified at StockX","seller_flex_quick_sale_discount_label":"Quick Sale Discount","seller_profile_learn_more_about_flex_pricing":"Learn more about Flex Pricing","seller_level_header":"Current Seller Level","seller_stockx_pro_message":"Use StockX Pro for professional tools like bulk listing, quick actions, and Sponsored Asks.","seller_bulk_ship_eligibility":"Bulk shipping has been disabled on your account. Please ","seller_bulk_ship_guidelines":"review our guidelines.","seller_credit_card_missing":"Please add a valid payment method in order to continue selling","seller_credit_card_missing_button":"Add Credit Card","seller_penalty_active_label":"Active","seller_penalty_inactive_label":"Waived","seller_penalty_applied_text":"Penalty applied next month","seller_penalty_exempt_text":"No change next month","seller_flake_penalty_tooltip":"If you do not ship {{targetRate}}% of your sales on time this month a {{percentageAmount}}% fee (min. ${{minDollarAmount}} USD) will be added to all orders next month that are not shipped on time. \u003c0\u003eLearn More\u003c/0\u003e","seller_flake_penalty_header":"Cancel Penalty Fee","seller_flake_penalty_active_description":"A {{percentageAmount}}% fee (min. ${{minDollarAmount}} USD) will be added to all orders this month that are not shipped on time. \u003c0\u003eLearn More\u003c/0\u003e","seller_flake_penalty_inactive_description":"You will not pay a penalty fee this month for orders that are not shipped. Items that do not meet our verification standards may still incur a penalty fee.","seller_profile_boosters_header":"Progress Toward Next Month’s Bonuses","seller_profile_booster_details":"StockX offers 2 additional ways to achieve a lower Seller Fee. Bonuses earned this month will be applied to your Seller Fee next month.","seller_profile_booster_flex_detail":"Only Standard sales are counted toward these bonuses. Flex sales always have a reduced seller fee.","seller_profile_greeting":"Hi, {{name}}","seller_profile_header":"Seller Level {{currentLevel}}","seller_profile_header_starndard_sales_label":"Standard Sales","seller_profile_header_flex_sales_label":"Flex Sales","seller_profile_revenue_label":"Sales ($)","seller_progress_bar_label":"{{remainingSalesRevenue}} or {{remainingSalesTotal}} sales \u003c0/\u003e\u003c1\u003eto unlock Level {{nextLevel}}\u003c/1\u003e","seller_progress_description":"Your activity during the current calendar quarter will determine your level in the next calendar quarter. Your Seller Level will reset on the first day of a new quarter, and you can level up at any time.","seller_progress_earning_period_days_left":"{{numberOfDays}} days left","seller_progress_footer":"Seller Levels are determined using USD at the time of sale. A sale is official once it has been paid out to the seller.","seller_progress_header":"Level Progress for Next Quarter","seller_progress_level_up_disclaimer":"You’ve achieved Level {{sellerLevel}} status for next quarter!","seller_progress_level_basic_disclaimer":"You're on track for Level {{sellerLevel}} status for next quarter!","seller_progress_not_on_track":"Not on track for next month.","seller_progress_on_track":"On track for next month","seller_ship_by_banner":"\u003c0\u003eyou must\u003c/0\u003e\u003c1/\u003eship items by {{date}}","Selling":"Selling","selling":"selling","SELLING":"SELLING","selling_bulk_shipping_announcement_banner_body":"We've compiled a checklist for you to make your bulk shipping process as simple as possible.","selling_bulk_shipping_announcement_banner_button":"Learn More","selling_bulk_shipping_announcement_banner_cta":"Select products below to create a bulk shipment","selling_bulk_shipping_announcement_heading":"New to Bulk Shipping?","selling_in_bulk_shipment":"Bulk Shipment","sell_flow_all_in_disclaimer":"Your Ask may appear higher due to local duties and taxes","sell_flow_australia_all_in_disclaimer":"Your Ask may appear higher due to local duties, VAT, and import fees","selling_fast_badge_text":"This product is selling fast","selling_fast_badge_secondary_text":"{{count}} Sold in Last 3 Days!","sell_low_demand_badge_title_v1":"Demand is Low","sell_low_demand_badge_title_v2":"Only {{amount}} Bids, Act Now ","sell_low_demand_badge_subtitle":"Only {{amount}} Buyers interested in this item.","sell_low_demand_badge_subtitle_no_bids":"There are no buyers interested in this item.","sell_high_inventory_badge_title_v1":"Inventory is High","sell_high_inventory_badge_title_v2":"Inventory is High, Act Fast","sell_high_inventory_badge_subtitle":"There are {{amount}} asks on this item.","sell_last_sale_badge_title":"Now {{amount}} Higher Than Last Sale","sell_average_price_badge_title":"Now {{amount}} Higher Than Average Price","September":"September","Set as Default Size":"Set as Default Size","Set Ask Price":"Set Ask Price","Settings":"Settings","settings_page_payout_with_paypal":"PayPal for {{sellerEmailAddress}}","Share":"Share","Share your Ask":"Share your Ask","Share your Bid":"Share your Bid","Share your Sale":"Share your Sale","Share your Purchase":"Share your Purchase","shop_with_confidence":"Shop with Confidence","shop_with_confidence_subtitle":"Every item purchased is verified by StockX or Xpress ships directly from a StockX Verified Seller. This ensures you get what you want, in the condition you expect.","Ship Today":"Ship Today","Shipment ID":"Shipment ID","shipment_generated_default_message":"Shipment is ready to print.","shipment_generation_complete_message":"Shipment {{displayId}} is ready to print.","shipment_footer_include_item_invoice":"Include this page inside the item’s original packaging","shipped":"shipped","shipped_on_time_rate_title":"Successful Ship Rate","success_rate_penalty_booster_description":"Ship at least {{targetRate}}% of this month’s sales on time to avoid cancel penalty fees next month.","success_rate_penalty_booster_description_v2":"Ship at least {{targetRate}}% of this month’s sales on time to avoid cancel penalty fees next month.","Shipping":"Shipping","SHIPPING":"SHIPPING","Shipping Address":"Shipping Address","Shipping Info":"Shipping Info","Shipping Instructions":"Shipping Instructions","shipping_cost_label":"Shipping Cost:","shipping_instructions_apparel_step_2":"Place the items into a bigger and sufficiently sized shipping box (not a polymailer) that is no more than 2 inches (5 cm) larger than your items on each side. Remove all pre-existing HAZMAT warnings, labels, and stickers from the shipping parcel.","shipping_instructions_apparel_step_3":"Use bubble wrap and/or packing paper to ensure your items are secure while in transit.","shipping_instructions_default_step_1":"Place this invoice inside the box and/or envelope with the product.","shipping_instructions_default_step_2":"Place the box and/or sleeve into a bigger and sufficiently sized shipping box that is no more than 2 inches (5 cm) larger than your item on each side. Remove all HAZMAT warnings, labels, and stickers from the shipping parcel.\n\n","shipping_instructions_default_step_3":"Use bubble wrap and/or packing paper to ensure your item is secure while in transit.","shipping_instructions_default_step_4":"\u003c0\u003eSeal package across the side flaps and the seams on the top and bottom of the shipping box using the 6 strip, H-method, with 2” or wider packing tape.\u003c/0\u003e Do not use masking tape, cellophane tape, duct tape, string or paper over-wrap to secure package.","shipping_instructions_default_step_5":"Tape or insert the StockX provided {{carrier}} label to the outside of your shipping box. Drop off your sealed package at an authorized {{carrier}} location to be sent off.","shipping_instructions_default_step_6":"Drop off your sealed package at an authorized {{carrier}} location to be sent off.","shipping_instructions_default_step_7":"As best practice, get a drop off receipt to ensure your package has been properly received.","shipping_instructions_hazmat_step_2":"\u003c0\u003ePlace the box and/or sleeve into a bigger and sufficiently sized shipping box that is no more than 2 inches (5 cm) larger than your item on each side. Remove all pre-existing HAZMAT warnings, labels, and stickers from the shipping parcel.\u003c/0\u003e\u003c0\u003e\u003c1\u003eNOTE –\u003c/1\u003e The box must meet IATA guidelines of being constructed of strong, rigid packaging that can pass a 1.2 meter drop test.\u003c/0\u003e","shipping_instructions_hazmat_step_5":"Tape or insert the StockX provided UPS label to the outside of your shipping box leaving enough space for the Lithium Ion Battery Handling Mark.","shipping_instructions_hazmat_step_6":"\u003c0\u003eTape or insert the StockX provided Lithium Ion Battery Handling Mark to the outside of your shipping box on the same side of the box as the shipping label.\u003c/0\u003e\u003c0\u003e\u003c1\u003eNOTE –\u003c/1\u003e The box must meet IATA guidelines of being constructed of strong, rigid packaging that can pass a 1.2 meter drop test.\u003c/0\u003e\u003c0\u003e\u003c1\u003eNOTE –\u003c/1\u003e Shipping Label \u0026 Lithium Ion Battery Handling Mark must be placed on same side of box or UPS will not accept package.\u003c/0\u003e\u003c0\u003e\u003c1\u003eNOTE –\u003c/1\u003e Shipping Label \u0026 Lithium Ion Battery Handling Mark must not be covered or obstructed in any form or fashion.\u003c/0\u003e","shipping_instructions_trading_card_step_1":"Bundle products should be grouped together in a sub-container within the Bulk Shipment large container. The invoice should also be inside the sub-container \u003c0\u003e(ex. contained within another box or polybag)\u003c/0\u003e.","shipping_instructions_trading_card_step_2":"Individual units (box, graded single, ungraded single, or miscellaneous), can be packed individually, with their invoice rubber banded around them.","shipping_label_hazmat_header":"Print in color and attach battery handling mark to the shipping box.","shipping_label_hazmat_subtext_1":"The Battery Handling Mark must be printed in color and attached to the same side of the box as the shipping label or UPS will not accept it. \u003c0\u003eFailure to comply may result in a canceled order and a penalty assessed to your account.\u003c/0\u003e","shipping_label_hazmat_subtext_2":"The mark must be at least 120 mm (4.7\") wide x 110 mm (4.3\") high in size. For small packages that have reduced surface space available it may be reduced to not less than 105 mm (4.1\") wide x 75 mm (3\") high in size.","shipping_label_instructions_page_one_header":"\u003c0\u003eInclude this\u003c/0\u003e \u003c0\u003epage inside\u003c/0\u003e \u003c0\u003ethe {{whereToPlaceInvoice}}.\u003c/0\u003e","shipping_label_instructions_page_one_header_other":"shipping box","shipping_label_instructions_page_one_header_sneakers":"sneaker box","shop_new_and_verified_no_amount":"Shop New and Verified","stockx_verification_available_at_checkout":"StockX Verification available at checkout","stockx_verification_title":"StockX Verification","stockx_verification_price":"StockX Verification - {{price}}","stockx_verification_description":"For added peace of mind, you can select StockX Verification for this item. Our team verifies the item to ensure it matches the seller's description.","stockx_verification_how_it_works_title":"How it Works:","stockx_verification_how_it_works":"The seller will first ship your item to StockX for verification. Once complete, it will be shipped to you. Please note, selecting this option will result in a longer delivery time for your item.","shop_new_and_verified":"Shop New and Verified from {{amount}}","shop_used_from":"Shop used from {{amount}}","ship_by_date":"Ship by {{date}}","Shoe":"Shoe","Shoe Size":"Shoe Size","Shoes":"Shoes","shoes":"shoes","Shoes \u0026 New Sneakers":"Shoes \u0026 New Sneakers","Show Less":"Show Less","Show More":"Show More","Sign Out":"Sign Out","Sign Up":"Sign Up","Sign Up Now":"Sign Up Now","Signout":"Signout","Signup":"Signup","signup":"signup","singapore_ddp_disclaimer":"If your order value is less than $280 USD, import duties and taxes will likely reduce to zero after order completion","single_doppelganger_pane_message":"The {{product}} is often confused with the {{similarProduct}}. Please check the product ID. If yours is different click on the button below to take you to the right product.","single_doppelganger_pane_title":"Hold the phone, this product has a doppelganger!","Size":"Size","Size Chart":"Size Chart","Sizes":"Sizes","Sizing:":"Sizing:","Skip":"Skip","Slow down speed racer":"Slow down speed racer","sneakers":"sneakers","Sneakers":"Sneakers","snowflake":"snowflake","social login":"social login","social_confirm_invalid_name":"Please enter a name without special characters.","social_confirm_first_name_is_required":"Please enter a first name.","social_confirm_last_name_is_required":"Please enter a last name.","social_confirm_email_is_required":"Please enter a valid email address.","sold":"sold","sold for":"sold for","sold_plural.one":"sold","sold_plural.other":"sold","Something went wrong":"Something went wrong","Something went wrong. Please try again later.":"Something went wrong. Please try again later.","Please try again":"Please try again.","Something went wrong fetching your pricing. Please try again":"Something went wrong fetching your pricing. Please try again","Sorry!":"Sorry!","Sorry!  There was an error on our end.  Please try again.":"Sorry!  The